skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mystic seer
des: Ask Mystic Seer a YES or NO question about your future. Just say things like "Ask Mystic Seer if I will win the lottery." But, be careful, some questions are best left unanswered. Mystic Seer is for amusement purposes only. Mystic Seer can't actually predict the future, as far as we know. If you'd like to build or purchase your own Mystic Seer replica visit mysticseer.com for more information.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
